  "title": "Maintenance Technician",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Implement and support machinery maintenance on Mechanical &amp; Electrical aspects  according to schedules.</li>\n  <li>Attend to breakdown, servicing, repairing, and urgent requests on equipment and facilities.</li>\n  <li>Record and report all faults, deficiencies, and other unusual occurrences, as well as the time and materials expended on work orders.</li>\n  <li>Perform  preventive maintenance work and any other duties as assigned by Superior.</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 2 years &amp; above.</li>\n</ul>",
